  <h2 class="content-h">The Challenge</h2>
  <div class="content-body">
    <p>A Bangladeshi e-commerce business processing ৳50M+ in annual sales across 12 product categories was drowning in spreadsheets. Their weekly sales reporting process took 4+ hours every Monday morning, involved 6 different Excel files, and was prone to errors that led to incorrect decisions.</p>
    <p>The operations manager reached out needing a single, reliable source of truth for their business performance data — something the entire team could access, understand, and trust.</p>
  </div>

